files.Title: ToSic.Cre8magic.OqtaneBasic.MagicContainer
files.Summary:
The recommended base container for all themes which use cre8magic.

It will simply remain invisible for the normal user, and except for a DIV containing some classes, it will not render anything.

Admin-users will see a bit more, since the title etc. is necessary for the editing tools.

files.Title: ToSic.Cre8magic.Pages.IMagicPage
files.Summary:
Magic Pages are smart wrappers around Oqtane Pages. They offer many benefits such as:

  1. Read-only properties (no accidental writing properties with unexpected side effects)
  2. Improved naming, e.g. .Id instead of .PageId
  3. Calculated properties such as Target (which becomes "_blank" for external links or null for normal links)
  4. Corrected values - e.g. the Link property will be javascript:void(0) if the page is not clickable
  5. Navigation properties such as Parent and Breadcrumb

files.Title: ToSic.Cre8magic.Utils.IgnoreEquals<TValue>
files.Summary:
Special helper to store a value on a record but not include it in the Equality contract.

Typical use case is calculated properties which contain the record itself, which would result in infinite loops.
